short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Lookup file extensions from FileInfo.com - The Central File Extensions Registry.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The File Extension Search chrome extension allows you to look up information about file extensions directly from the Google Chrome toolbar.  Simply click the FileInfo.com icon and type an extension in the search box.  It is an easy way to look up information about downloaded files before you open them.
